item.title: CVE-2021-32456|2024-09-17T04:14:29.511Z -- sitel -- cap%2Fprx
item.description: SITEL CAP/PRX firmware version 5.2.01 allows an attacker with access to the local network of the device to obtain the authentication passwords by analysing the network traffic.
